网络客户端工具:
	ping/ftp/lftp/lftpget/wget

----------------------------------------------------------------
		ping
----------------------------------------------------------------
ping -send ICMP ECHO_REQUEST to network hosts
-c # :发送的包的个数
-w #:ping命令超时时长
-W # : ping的时长
-s # : 发送数据包的大小
----------------------------------------------------------------
		hping 
----------------------------------------------------------------
send (almost) arbitraryTCP/IP packets to network hosts 
	 --fast 
	 --faster 
	 --flood 
	 --i uX
----------------------------------------------------------------
		traceroute
----------------------------------------------------------------
	-pring the route packages trace to network hosts
	
----------------------------------------------------------------
		ftp
----------------------------------------------------------------
file transfer protocol client 
ftp服务的命令行客户端程序

----------------------------------------------------------------
		lftp
----------------------------------------------------------------
	get
	mget
	put
	mput
	
----------------------------------------------------------------
 		lftpget
----------------------------------------------------------------
	lftpget[-c][-d][-v]URL [URL...]
	-c 断点续传 
----------------------------------------------------------------
		wget
----------------------------------------------------------------
wget [option]...[URL]...
	-b : 在后台执行下载操作;
	-q : quiet
	-O file : 下载文件保存的位置;
	-c : 续传;
	--limit-rate=amount ; 一指定的速率传输文件
